      <conclusions>
         <blockContainer class="explanatoryNotes">
            <heading>EXPLANATORY NOTE</heading>
            <block name="comment">(This note is not part of the Regulations)</block>
            <p>These Regulations provide 100% relief from business rates to any provider of new fibre infrastructure for telecommunication. The relief is available for a 10 year period until 31 March 2029.</p>
            <p>An application must be made to obtain the relief and regulation 4 sets out how applications are to be made.</p>
         </blockContainer>
